  "lastNarrative": "On the wind‑swept plains, the Archmage lingered, eyes flicking for a crack in the enemy’s shield. At the strike of the first round, test 2 seized the moment, channeling a torrent of arcane fire that ripped through the ranks. The foes crumbled in a blaze of light, the final scream echoing as the last adversary fell. Victory roared across the battlefield, and the hero surged upward, leveling anew as the plains fell silent.",
